{"tid":2149032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞超最期待：4秒4中柱 情越白界線 打機式唔入","createTime":"2020-08-10T07:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T12:37:54.000Z","uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a67bae642c01d6d9aafe778830839cb489e385e0","tid":2149032,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200810/369457523939479552.png/JeKIimNYPt0ALD7SiH5OWAIjTXYx0qJcrwIOpq8CDqY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200810%2F369457523939479552.png%2FJeKIimNYPt0ALD7SiH5OWAIjTXYx0qJcrwIOpq8CDqY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dbb7d306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下游球隊科根堡（Falkenbergs）主場迎戰榜首的馬模，開賽已經風起雲湧。馬模前鋒艾錫泰連（Isaac THELIN）跟科根堡後衛互有動作，沉不住氣一腳踢向對手，於8分鐘紅牌直接驅逐。馬模十人應戰，兩分鐘後卻先開紀錄。失球後1分鐘，科根堡反撲，上演「掟手掣」一幕。<br />\n <br />\n科根堡策動反擊，中場兩下斜傳已撕破馬模後防，接應球員立即燙射，令馬模門將鞭長莫及。射門卻彈中內柱，<span class=\"gold\">沿着白界線一路滾，再中另一邊內柱。球速慢下來，仍繼續沿着白界滾動。</span>雙方球員立即衝前。馬模後衛先一步趕到，在白界線上拗腰解圍。科根堡球員伸腳搏反彈入網，皮球果然省中小腿，可惜只差一點點，彈中柱面。更不幸的是，這<span class=\"gold\">名科根堡球員「食波餅」後，皮球又反彈，再次彈中柱面，他「人前波後」盡力伸腳，反把皮球踢走。短短4秒間，科根堡連中4次柱</span>，可算「黑過墨斗」。<br />\n<br />\n馬模化險為夷，捱過科根堡大舉反撲，結果全場大部分時間以寡敵眾下，以1：0險勝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ndd3A_eaPKU?t=53\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fndd3A_eaPKU%3Ft%3D53&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=2cf445ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ndd3A_eaPKU?t=53</a>"},{"pid":"5a5cec67835a4bd38e3f4738ab873301ecd4b615","tid":2149032,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"睇描述已經笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9b9a7f63fef98d55493cda389845c19f4afd8d","tid":2149032,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde07ef3f8ff86cf80d5b90f42d22955ab94